    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available for acquisition is a driver-focused E46 M3, featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six powerplant equipped with individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system. This unit delivers linear power delivery up to its 8,000 RPM redline, mated to a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. Mechanical integrity is prioritized, with the rear subframe mounting points reinforced and the rod bearings recently addressed\u2014essential preventative maintenance for this chassis. The suspension geometry remains tight, utilizing a MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear setup with a torque-sensing M-Variable limited-slip differential. While the exterior shows minor evidence of its enthusiast-driven history, the aerodynamic profile remains striking. This is a mechanically robust example of BMW\u2019s high-revving naturally aspirated era, ready for spirited canyon carving or track-day duty.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
