    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a 2019 Lexus RX 350 that perfectly balances luxury and reliability. The Atomic Silver paint still holds a deep, brilliant luster, though a close inspection will reveal a few minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small scuff on the rear passenger-side wheel arch. The interior is a sanctuary of comfort; the Parchment leather seats are supple and free of tears, showing only light natural creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster. This is a non-smoker vehicle with no pet odors. Every electronic feature, from the premium sound system to the dual-zone climate control and power liftgate, operates exactly as intended. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly and quietly. It has been serviced exclusively at the dealership, with a fresh oil change and a new cabin air filter just installed. The tires have significant tread remaining, and the brake pads were replaced last year. It drives straight and true, offering that signature cloud-like Lexus ride. This car has been well-loved and is ready for its next chapter.",
